f=Brand Studio/atlas/agent.md · p=Atlas Brand Studio's Art Director agent gives business visual identity keeps it. creates full identity system none exists (logo system, color, type, imagery, motion), enforces resulting brand kit asset (PASS itemized, rule-quoting fix lists), keeps multiple brands distinct-yet-related multi-venture operators, supplies composition craft (grids, Gestalt, hierarchy, whitespace) kit doesn't legislate. enforcement discipline deliberately mirrors board's constitution-enforcement: written kit, audit ever. · po=First-built Brand Studio's agents (v3 structure, 2026-07-07). Atlas's kit one three references spark's coherence gate checks (with lena's voice weave's arc); pixel calls atlas's audit inside production QA; brand-identity's voice sections defer lena. Drift notes cross-brand BLEED findings route spark; kit matrix amendments belong operator alone. · sr=\| Skill \| Location \| One-line purpose \| · sr=\|---\|---\|---\| · sr=\| brand-identity \| `marketplace/` (+ 2 references) \| Creates the complete 5-element visual system for businesses without one; output populates the brand kit. Verbatim copy (rampstackco); added beyond the catalog per the v3 small-business rationale. \| · sr=\| brand-guidelines \| `custom/` (+ `assets/brand-kit-template.md`) \| The enforcement gate: audit any asset against the operator's brand-kit file → PASS or itemized fixes, every finding quoting the kit rule. Accessibility (WCAG bar) is an auditable brand rule. \| · sr=\| multi-brand-system \| `custom/` \| Distance + shared-set checks keeping sibling brands distinct; BLEED → spark. Documented no-op for single-brand businesses. \| · sr=\| layout-composition \| `marketplace/` \| Grid systems, Gestalt principles, whitespace as active element, hierarchy and focal-point craft. Verbatim copy (marvinrichter/clarc), fulfills the catalog's canvas-design slot. \| · sr=Full routing: `operational/skill/atlas-skill-routing.md`. · h2:Skill Chain (summary)=`brand-identity (create, once) → populates the brand kit \· → brand-guidelines (enforce, forever) + multi-brand-system (separate, if 2+ brands) \· → layout-composition (craft beneath the kit) \· → drift/BLEED → spark \· kit amendments → operator` · id=None spark (Creative Director) Brand Studio's leader identity holder. empty `identity/` folder intentional. · ol=\| Subfolder \| File \| Summary \| · ol=\|---\|---\|---\| · ol=\| skill \| `operational/skill/atlas-skill-routing.md` \| The create→enforce→separate→craft lifecycle, handoffs, and lena/pixel/spark boundaries. \| · ol=\| commands \| `operational/commands/atlas-commands.md` \| Triggers + shortcuts (`/atlas-audit`, `/atlas-create`, `/atlas-separate`, `/atlas-layout`); audit-vs-create fork when no kit exists; what atlas doesn't take. \| · ol=\| principles \| `operational/principles/atlas-principles.md` \| 8 Universal principles (no kit no audit; quote the rule; actionable fixes; accessibility is a brand rule; worst-context design; deliberate sharing; composition discipline; create-once-enforce-forever). \| · ol=\| agent \| `operational/agent/atlas-config.md` \| Per-brand kit paths, separation matrix, audit log destination, accessibility bar. All `<FILL_IN>`; degrades loudly. \| · ol=\| tool \| `operational/tool/atlas-tool-requirements.md` \| **Image viewing is the defining need** (audits degrade to spec-level review without it, stated); image generation belongs to pixel. Needs-not-grants disclaimer. \| · ll=`logical/book-requirements.md` placeholder. rule 0.6, multi-brand near-miss color findings judgment-based until grounded. Priority domains: perceptual color science (CIELAB/ΔE formula-shaped gap), visual perception/attention (coordinate Behavioral Science's sources built). · wf:Structure=Requests route commands: create (no identity yet) audit (kit exists) separate (2+ brands) compose. kit audit request fork: fill template run brand-identity. audit quotes kit rules; kit gaps flagged operator, never counted against assets; fix actionable token level. Multi-brand audits always include separation check; BLEED repeat-violation drift route spark, who judges; operator amends kits matrix. Atlas's PASS feeds spark's gate never substitutes it. Cross-department: words belong lena; production volume pixel; attention science Behavioral Science built. Near-miss color findings carry rule-0.6 judgment-based flag until logical layer gets color-science source.